text: Syntar Klas Sunn is an Indian politician from Meghalaya. He is a member of the United Democratic Party. He was elected from East Khasi Hills district's Mawphlang assembly constituency of Meghalaya in 2018 as an Independent politician but later joined United Democratic Party.Meghalaya Democratic Alliance strength rises to 39My NetaSK Sunn elected President of Shillong Sports Association ==References== Category:Living people Category:Members of the Meghalaya Legislative Assembly Category:United Democratic Party (Meghalaya) politicians Category:People from East Khasi Hills district Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Meghalaya MLAs 2018–
